Overview & Integration Options
Spotify offers two primary integration patterns for yHealth. Understanding which approach to use before starting development will save significant time and prevent architectural mistakes.

Option A — OAuth User Connect	Option B — Curated Playlists (Free Tier)
User links their own Spotify account	App curates playlists via Client Credentials
Access to personal saved songs, playlists, history	No user login required
Requires Spotify Premium for full playback	Limited to 30-sec previews only
Best for: personalization, favourites sync	Best for: preset workout / meditation playlists
Scope: user-library-read, user-top-read, streaming	Scope: no user scope needed

Recommendation for yHealth
Implement BOTH options. Use Option B to offer in-app health playlists immediately (zero friction), while Option A lets users who have Spotify Premium unlock their personal library and favourites for a fully personalised experience.




